chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都一定會有一定既fans入去聽佢去國語歌</blockquote><br />\n可能佢覺得係死忠既已經會自動去深圳/廣州場睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW Another Eason's Life連澳門威尼斯人都有去，講真佢租個紅館/博覽館開個香港站演唱會，就算佢山頂嗰排賣 $750都仍然可以爆到好多場，就係死唔肯返香港開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n麥花臣吹水+ 唱十幾首左右極速散水既新碟宣傳showcase就夠膽收人 $750 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccac2fa36bf3045ddfdef801b5f65d20ce1257ef","tid":386264,"uid":45957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:37:42.000Z","msg":"成個9月唱哂成個大陸咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n10月黎到香港又爛聲<br />\n又話休息下 出隻碟又要搞個世界巡迴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6323293d604890be93ab1a842a7f561e8d424d","tid":386264,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:14:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.seetickets.com/event/eason-says-c-mon-in-tour-by-touch-music-live-2017/queen-elizabeth-olympic-park/1133710?lang=da\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.seetickets.com%2Fevent%2Feason-says-c-mon-in-tour-by-touch-music-live-2017%2Fqueen-elizabeth-olympic-park%2F1133710%3Flang%3Dda&d=d1%2FAf9e1WbMxd7nKXcPtMTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=10e90a52\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.seetickets.com/event/eason-says-c-mon-in-tour-by-touch-music-live-2017/queen-elizabeth-olympic-park/1133710?lang=da</a><br />\nLondon站要一百一十磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c84875ac194df69c7cd3178df373cd03c8e098","tid":386264,"uid":38203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T11:00:52.000Z","msg":"要排隊買？ 售票網唔見有"}]}